{"tid":2418092,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聖誕節和你Shop推撞警長襲警罪成 活動助理判囚4星期","createTime":"2021-02-22T10:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T12:00:22.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"31b93c791b9aacc3718b7d765050bab4d4ada92c","tid":2418092,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:59:40.000Z","msg":"前年12月25日聖誕節「和你Shop」行動期間，三名青年被指在沙田新城市廣場襲警及非法集結，案件經審訊後，裁判官李志豪早前裁定27歲活動助理襲警罪成。案件今判刑，李官閱畢被告的背景報告後，判他入獄4星期。<br />\n<br />\n李官曾明言本案在社會事件的氛圍下發生，被告遭判囚無可避免。辯方今同意判監為合適決定，惟求情時指出本案的襲擊並不嚴重，被告只是<span class=\"red\">對警員「推咗一下」，亦無造成傷害</span>。辯方又指不能排除是警長跑走時匆忙間撞到別人，以致被告作出後來的行為。"},{"pid":"72129260e000f9a5dabab856f2db5291b550d946","tid":2418092,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:59:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/YEQNNB5ZWJFP5LG6AGUKB2ZOGY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2FYEQNNB5ZWJFP5LG6AGUKB2ZOGY%2F&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2Xnr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=5c08c1c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2FYEQNNB5ZWJFP5LG6AGUKB2ZOGY%2F&h=ca34d3be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/YEQNNB5ZWJFP5LG6AGUKB2ZOGY/</a>"},{"pid":"c16a6d766fd664113dd78743743ee53a1446b620","tid":2418092,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T11:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1babb2870d589160ff3df9381109e4fd4f4b61d7","tid":2418092,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T11:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2d5ff4a11e42e24a80344359b64a1d7e59a6c5","tid":2418092,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T11:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"